params.leafIndex: The index of the message in the L2 block's message tree
params.siblingPath: Merkle proof path from leaf to root

Send L1->L2 confirmation message Privacy: Uses ownerHash instead of owner address to prevent identity linkage

params.l2BlockNumber: The L2 block number where the message was created
